/PGPRAYER FOR THOSE WHO ARE ILL/XX686/XX/PR

/KAA PRAYER FOR ALL THOSE WHO ARE ILL/PR

AND THEIR CARETAKERS/XX/PR

May the One who blesses all Life, bless and heal/PR

these people who struggle against illness./PR

/PR

May those afflicted with disease be blessed with/PR

faith, courage, loving and caring. May they know/PR

much support and sustenance from their friends,/PR

their loving companions and their communities./PR

/PR

May they be granted a full and/PR

complete healing of body and soul./PR

/PR

May those who seek ways of healing through/PR

increased medical knowledge and those who care for/PR

the sick daily be blessed with courage,/PR

stamina and communal support./PR

/PR

May all, the sick and the well together, be granted/PR

courage and hope. And let us say: Amen./PR

Leila Gal Berner/XX/PR

