May the one who blessed our ancestors, Abraham, Isaac, and
Jacob, Sarah, Rebekah, Rachel, and Leah, bless 
who is making aliyah to /ITEretz Yisrael/XX, (together with his / her
family) in order to establish a home there. May he / she journey
there in peace and settle safely in the Land of Zion. May he / she
find blessing and success in all he / she undertakes there.
"Whoever among you, (wishes to settle there), may the God of
Israel be with that person--let him / her go up to the Land!"
And let us say: Amen./PR

